Name: ENABLE
Description: The item is enabled and operational.

Name: PROCESSING
Description: The item is currently being processed.

Name: QUEUED
Description: The item is in the queue.

Name: COMPLETED
Description: The process or task associated with the item has been completed.

Name: FAILED
Description: The process or task associated with the item has failed.

Name: CANCELLED
Description: The process or task associated with the item has been cancelled.
